te markers suggest that both species are clonal and likely represent recently-introduced strains. Intensive research is underway to develop rapid screening protocols for early detection of the pathogens and management strategies in an attempt to prevent the spread of the pathogens to the other islands of Hawai'i, which are currently disease free.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Barnes, I.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Fourie, A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Wingfield, M.J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Harrington, T.C.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "McNew, D.L.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Sugiyama, L.S.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Luiz, B.C.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Heller, W.P.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Keith, L.M.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Chapter 4", "biodiversity", "environment assessment", "IPBES", "Alien Invasive Species Assessment AIS", "invasive species"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/5cb880d647dd85e593c0473c63e5bd4e", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/86c556757835b67cd6897d8eae62c8541cb4aff979ea6cef827b6f7b2cf522fe", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/2352922/items/8GCWY8LJ", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/2352922/items/8GCWY8LJ", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/5ccf0b6f95c2f6b6fa357c7693277e8c!/b35951-38097", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/359bd494433933b868f85e88d3437f76", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.3767/persoonia.2018.40.07", "relation": "isVariantFormOf", "resource_type": "publication", "scheme": "doi"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.7430682", "relation": "isCitedBy", "resource_type": "publication-report", "scheme": "doi"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "rel